lead_paragraph: Nine days ago, Zhang Shuai was nearly on a plane back to China before the Australian Open began. The French veteran Virginie Razzano was serving for the match against her in the final round of qualifying, but Zhang was able to break back and win the third set 8-6 — along with a spot in the main draw.

headline.print_headline: Zhang's Run Continues With 4th-Round Win Over Injured Keys
